snippet.title: Gravity Falls - Theme Song [Electro Swing Remix]
snippet.description:
Gravity Falls Presents: The Dapper Dipper and The Marvelous Mabel

It's been a while since I've made a song. I have too much stuff going on right now. Also, that glitch at 1:12 is not supposed to be there. Window's Movie Maker's rendering sucks :/

I added some parts from "Made me realize" too.
